<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>A Small Surprise ✨</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}
body{
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(-45deg,#ffd6e7,#ffe6f2,#fff1c9,#ffd6e7);
background-size:400% 400%;
animation:bg 10s ease infinite;
}
@keyframes bg{
0%{background-position:0% 50%;}
50%{background-position:100% 50%;}
100%{background-position:0% 50%;}
}
.card{
width:90%;
max-width:950px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
padding:40px;
border-radius:30px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
animation:fadeIn 1.5s ease;
position:relative;
z-index:2;
}
h1{
font-size:48px;
color:#ff4f8b;
margin-bottom:20px;
text-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(255,79,139,.4);
}
p{
font-size:19px;
line-height:1.9;
color:#444;
}
button{
margin-top:25px;
padding:12px 30px;
border:none;
border-radius:50px;
background:#ff4f8b;
color:white;
font-size:17px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}
button:hover{
transform:scale(1.08);
}
#surprise{
display:none;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:22px;
color:#ff4f8b;
font-weight:600;
}
.heart{
position:absolute;
color:#ff4f8b;
font-size:25px;
animation:float 8s linear infinite;
opacity:.7;
}
@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
opacity:0;
}
20%{
opacity:1;
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-120vh);
opacity:0;
}
}
.photo{
margin:20px auto;
width:180px;
height:180px;
border-radius:50%;
overflow:hidden;
border:5px solid #ffb6cf;
box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}
.photo img{
width:100%;
height:100%;
object-fit:cover;
}
@keyframes fadeIn{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(30px);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="heart" style="left:10%">❤️</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:25%;animation-delay:2s">💖</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:45%;animation-delay:4s">🌸</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:65%;animation-delay:1s">💗</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:85%;animation-delay:3s">✨</div>
<div class="card">
<h1>✨ Hey Shaily ✨</h1>
<div class="photo">
<img src="YOUR_IMAGE_URL_HERE" alt="Photo">
</div>
<p>
Ye bas ek chhota sa surprise hai 😊. Kaafi din se coding practice nahi ki thi, toh socha kuch creative banaya jaye aur pata nahi kyun ye banate waqt tum yaad aa gayi 😄. Is page ka koi hidden meaning nahi hai aur na hi tumhe awkward feel karane ka koi intention hai, bas itna sa hai ki agar ye dekh kar tumhare face par ek smile aa jaye toh meri mehnat successful maan lunga ✨. Thank you un random conversations, funny moments, unexpected calls, snaps aur un chhoti chhoti baaton ke liye jo kabhi kabhi poore din ka mood achha kar deti hain. Shayad tumhe andaaza bhi na ho, lekin tumhari positive vibe aur energy kaafi achhi lagti hai 🌷😊. Bas hamesha khush rehna, apne goals achieve karna aur aise hi smile karte rehna, kyunki genuinely smile tum par bahut achhi lagti hai 💖.
</p>

Click Here 😄

<div id="surprise">
🌸 Thank You For Being You 🌸
</div>
<audio id="music" loop>
<source src="YOUR_MUSIC_LINK.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>
</div>
<script>
function showSurprise(){
document.getElementById("surprise").style.display="block";
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
